name: Metadataremover
tagline: Android App to remove images metadata
body:
### Metadata Remover
This project started because I couldn't find any app to remove metadata from images, because of that reason it has a simple design maybe in the future it gets an awesome one.
Developed in Java with Android Studio, three single buttons with its case in the onClick.


### Support or Contact
Want to help? 
You can send suggestions to ifrey att protonmail.ch 
You can help for the design, or enhance the gallery button.
